'''Nicolás Capaldo Taboas''' (born 14 September 1998) is an Argentine professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for {{German football updater|Hamburg}} club [[Hamburger SV]] and the [[Argentina national football team|Argentina national team]].<ref name="Soccerway">{{Soccerway|nicolas-capaldo/592360}}</ref>

==Club career==
Capaldo is a product of the [[Boca Juniors]] academy, he had been signed from Deportivo Mac Allister in 2015.<ref name="La Arena">{{cite news|title="Es un sueño que estoy cumpliendo"|url=http://www.laarena.com.ar/deportes-es-un-sueno-que-estoy-cumpliendo-2032702-116.html|accessdate=25 February 2019|work=La Arena|date=7 January 2019}}</ref><ref name="La Nación">{{cite news|title=Así formará Boca en el primer partido de Gustavo Alfaro: tres debuts en el amistoso ante Unión|url=https://www.lanacion.com.ar/2211368-el-primer-equipo-gustavo-alfaro-asi-formara|accessdate=25 February 2019|work=La Nación|date=16 January 2019|archive-date=3 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203204943/https://www.lanacion.com.ar/2211368-el-primer-equipo-gustavo-alfaro-asi-formara|url-status=dead}}</ref> [[Gustavo Alfaro]] called the midfielder up in 2019, initially for the mid-season break where he featured in a [[Torneos de Verano (Argentina)|Torneo de Verano]] friendly with [[Unión de Santa Fe|Unión Santa Fe]] on 16 January.<ref name="Soccerway"/> After not being used while on the substitutes bench for away fixtures with [[San Martín de San Juan|San Martín]] and [[Club Atlético Belgrano|Belgrano]], Capaldo made his debut in professional football during a [[Argentine Primera División|Primera División]] match against [[Defensa y Justicia]] on 24 February at the [[Estadio Norberto "Tito" Tomaghello]].<ref name="Soccerway"/><ref name="Infobae">{{cite news|title=Quiénes son las promesas que llevó Alfaro a la pretemporada de Boca y qué lugar les dará|url=https://www.infobae.com/deportes-2/2019/01/08/quienes-son-las-promesas-que-llevo-alfaro-a-la-pretemporada-de-boca-y-que-lugar-les-dara/|accessdate=25 February 2019|work=Infobae|date=8 January 2019}}</ref><ref name="Diario Popular">{{cite news|title=¿Quién es este pibe que encantó a Alfaro?|url=https://www.diariopopular.com.ar/quien-es-este-pibe-que-encanto-alfaro-n381970|accessdate=25 February 2019|work=Diario Popular|date=11 January 2019}}</ref>

On 10 July 2025, after four seasons with [[Austrian Football Bundesliga|Austrian Bundesliga]] club [[FC Red Bull Salzburg|Red Bull Salzburg]], Capaldo moved to Germany, joining [[Bundesliga]] club [[Hamburger SV]] permanently, for a €4.5 million estimated fee.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.redbullsalzburg.at/en/recent/news/nicolas-capaldo-transfer-hsv|title=Nicolas Capaldo moves to the German Bundesliga}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=Hamburger SV|url=https://www.hsv.de/en/hsv-sign-nicolas-capaldo|title=HSV sign Nicolas Capaldo|date=10 July 2025|access-date=12 July 2025}}</ref>

==International career==
In September 2019, Capaldo was called up by the [[Argentina national under-23 football team|Argentina U23s]] ahead of an exhibition fixture with Bolivia.<ref name="AFA1">{{cite news|title=La Selección Sub 23 jugará ante Bolivia desde las 19, en el estadio de Banfield|url=https://www.afa.com.ar/es/posts/la-seleccion-sub-23-enfrentara-a-bolivia-desde-las-19-en-el-estadio-de-banfield|accessdate=4 September 2019|work=AFA|date=3 September 2019|archive-date=19 November 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119141250/https://www.afa.com.ar/es/posts/la-seleccion-sub-23-enfrentara-a-bolivia-desde-las-19-en-el-estadio-de-banfield|url-status=live}}</ref> He played his first match a few days later against Colombia, and scored his first goal for the team against Brazil in a 1–0 win for the Gran Canaria invitational tournament final.

==Personal life==
Born and raised in Argentina, Capaldo is of Italian descent.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/da-capaldo-e-valentini-a-maestro-puch-tutti-gli-oriundi-nel-mirino-di-mancini-per-l-italia-1808130|title=Da Capaldo e Valentini a Maestro Puch: tutti gli oriundi nel mirino di Mancini per l'Italia - TUTTOmercatoWEB.com|website=www.tuttomercatoweb.com}}</ref>

